# ðŸŽ® Task 03: Tic-Tac-Toe Web Application

## Objective
Create an interactive **Tic-Tac-Toe web application** that can be played between two users or against a computer.

## Task Description
- Implement a classic tic-tac-toe game with:
  - User click handling.
  - Game state tracking.
  - Logic to detect winning conditions and draws.
- Optional: Add AI for playing against the computer.

## Features
- Two-player mode (and optionally vs computer).
- Real-time win/draw detection.
- Highlight winning moves.
- Responsive and engaging user interface.

## Technologies Used
- HTML
- CSS
- JavaScript

